        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lustrous stands in front of the window of the observatory, looking out at the lifeless seaborne city.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The more one thing has shone, the more forsaken it looks when it falls.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Too long has passed. Everyone she knows has passed. Now, standing here alone, she looks like a wavering torch in a storm.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'And this last torch is about to go out.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The weather is not great today. Dark clouds cover the sky, but the rain has yet to fall. Literal silver linings are peeking from between the clouds.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lustrous', 3: '...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She closes her eyes, trying to feel the warmth on her cheeks.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lustrous', 3: 'So in the end, I still have that speck of weakness in me...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lustrous', 3: 'Oh, brain, I despise you sometimes.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lustrous sighs softly.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She has never shown any weakness in front of others because she was their flag.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A flag is a symbol and a metaphor. A flag does not need to show humanity or have a heart. A flag just needs to be hung before an army during wars and planted on the enemy\\'s castle after victory.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'As long as the flag does not fall, everyone else will charge toward the same destination. As long as it stands, everyone will march forward fearlessly for their dreams and beliefs.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But now, everyone she was leading is gone. They have burnt their dignity and soul into cinders for their last act for humanity.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'And so, the flag becomes a human again.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lustrous', 3: 'Try to stay away as long as I can...?'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lustrous', 3: 'I\\'m afraid I can\\'t keep that promise.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The observatory used to be where they liked to stay the most.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'It sits at the top of Atlantis, and they could see the whole city from here. They could see the ocean, the sky, the stars.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The observatory is empty now. She is the only one left, trying to see humanity\\'s future.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lustrous walks to her chair and sits down.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She has done her job. This is as far as she goes.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She is tired.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She will leave the rest of the work to those who come after.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lustrous turns around and takes one last look at the setting sun.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 62,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Just one regret—she thinks.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 62,
        "ActionId": 63,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The day she set foot on this island, she thought she would go to the edge of the universe one day.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 63,
        "ActionId": 64,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lustrous', 3: 'Who would have thought that, in the end, I\\'d go gentle into that good night?'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 64,
        "ActionId": 65,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Her last whisper is carried away by the wind, disappearing with the last hint of sunlight.'}"
    },
